    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1883-10-21T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1883-10-21T00:00:00-05:00" n="453" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d453">
                <head>No. 454.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Phelps</persName>
                            to Mr. <persName type="to">Frelinghuysen</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of
                                    the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Lima</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1883-10-21">
                            <hi rend="italic">October</hi> 21,
                        1883</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Treaty has been signed. Chili has recognized Iglesias as President through
                        her minister for foreign affairs.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>PHELPS.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
